			<div class="content" id="post-content-2365515">
									

<p>Thanks for all the work that went into this. When I joined this site about a hundred (6) years ago, it was after hearing about it through a Something Awful GBS forum thread. That once well-moderated forum has gone all wonky, but SCP continues to maintain high standards both in content and in forum/comment thread interaction, and the mods definitely deserve a huge chunk of credit for that. Balancing high standards and a welcoming, nurturing, creative vibe is not easy. I love this place. Here's to another hundred (or whatever) years!</p>

