														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2365825">
									

<p>There's a difference between content warnings and trigger warnings, I have PTSD and I still enjoy horror as a genre, but I do prefer not to be surprised by gunfire and explosions. It isn't unreasonable for somebody to still want to enjoy horror stories while avoiding specific common traumatic triggers.</p>
<p>Whether it is feasible here given the format is debatable, but the request in and of itself isn't unreasonable.</p>

